📘 Design Ideas
	🔗 Nginx Configuration Guide (Official)
	https://nginx.org/en/docs/beginners_guide.html
	Understand how Nginx processes server and location blocks.

🔗 Nginx Request Processing Flowchart (GitHub)
	Visual explanation of how requests flow through virtual servers and locations.

💡 For UML/Classes
		Think of the Router as a dispatcher with:
		Server matching: Host + port
		Location matching: longest path prefix
		Method enforcement